OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fbecoming less frequent for a time into
OL,7,Fthe evening, before returning later in
OL,8,Fthe night, perhaps merging to give
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain by dawn. Feeling
OL,10,Fcool still with winds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FShowery outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Facross the region in the morning.
OL,14,FThese easing into the afternoon to
OL,15,Fallow a greater number of sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Feeling cool and breezy,
OL,17,Fespecially along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
