OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWet
OL,6,Fand windy weather moves in for
OL,7,FThursday. Largely cloudy on Friday
OL,8,Fwith patchy rain. High pressure
OL,9,Fdeveloping from Saturday with sunny
OL,10,Fspells, but low cloud and fog along
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
